reviews.text: Isquare  Is a nice shopping mall it has really call art work in front of it. It's really busy has a lot of nice shops that are all open past 10:00 p.m. It's in a convenient location from the Subway. Has some good restaurants in it. And the movie theater

It's a modern and great design shopping center and close to my hotel. I went here for a lunch and found Mark & Spencer on the ground floor and shopped a bit here. Overall, it's a nice shopping center.
Good for shopping (M&S clothing and food hall, marketplace), kids-r-us and other kid brands, very good cinema, linked to TST MTR train station
Visited the EyeLounge.  Very nice location with breath taking views of the city! Good drinks and very nice restaurant and cuisine.
High end shopping mall in Kowloon. Big brands.
